ports.behavior:

assign ContainedClassification.Low if Level.Low

forward a_media

assign Level.High if Level.High from alice_browser_id,a_media,bob_browser_id,b_port

forward a_media_package

forward encr_bob_session_data

forward alice_browser_id

assign Level.High if Level.High from alice_browser_id,a_port,b_media,bob_browser_id

forward b_media_package

assign ContainedClassification.Low if Level.Low
set Level.Low

forward encr_b_media
assign Level.High if ContainedClassification.High
unset ContainedClassification.High

forward encr_alice_session_data
assign Level.High if ContainedClassification.High
unset ContainedClassification.High

forward encr_a_media
assign Level.High if ContainedClassification.High
unset ContainedClassification.High
